edu.smcm.ai.tictactoe

Class TicTacToeState

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.smcm.ai.search.State
      • edu.smcm.ai.search.AdversarialState
        • edu.smcm.ai.tictactoe.TicTacToeState

  • public class TicTacToeState
extends AdversarialState
    State of a TicTacToe board. Implementation of the actual state of a Tic Tac Toe board. The board can be of any (square) size. Many of the methods are pass-throughs from @see TicTacToeGame. This is done for modularity reasons. The rules of the game are described in "Artificial Intelligence: A Modern Approach" (Third Edition) by Russell and Norvig on p. 162.
